snippet.title: Rise Online World - Official Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Rise Online World will be officially released on 15.04.2022.

A thrilling adventure, an MMORPG that you will love and have fun, combination of oldschool and modern MMORPG, a magical world where you fight for your kingdom and become a legend! 
----
Rise Online World; Nefes kesen bir macera, eski ve modern rol yapma oyunlarının kombinasyonu, krallığınız için savaşıp bir efsane olabileceğiniz büyülü bir dünya. 

Website: https://www.riseonlineworld.com
Forum: https://forum.riseonlineworld.com
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/RiseOnlineWorld
Twitter: https://twitter.com/RiseOnlineWorld
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/riseonlineworld
Discord: https://www.riseonlineworld.com/discord
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/riseonlineworld 
Twitch Category: https://www.twitch.tv/directory/game/Rise%20Online

Album: Forces
Composer: Erick Devore
Music: Infinite Climb

Follow us to get the latest news about the game. 

Contact info@riseonlineworld.com
